flowchart LR
    A[Developer Commit] --> B[GitHub Push / Pull Request]
    B --> C[GitHub Actions Workflow]
    C --> D[Checkout Repository]
    D --> E[Install Security Tooling]
    E --> F[Semgrep Scan]
    F --> G[pip-audit Scan]
    G --> H[Checkov Scan]
    H --> I{Dockerfile present?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Build Container Image]
    J --> K[Trivy Image Scan]
    I -- No --> L[Skip Image Scan]
    K --> M[Generate SBOM with Syft]
    L --> M
    M --> N[Upload Scan Artifacts]
    M --> O[Upload SBOM to Dependency-Track]
    N --> P[Import Findings to DefectDojo]
    O --> Q[Continuous Component Monitoring]
    P --> R[Triaged and Tracked Findings]
    Q --> R
